description: Description: Toxother column is a Depocity study including Somnolence, Arachnoiditis, Leucoencephalopathy, Unbearable paresthesia, Grade 3-4 neurotox. not rel. to others, Psychosis, and Cognitive deficits related to childhood Leukemia cancer treatment.
